Key Skills for Reading: Letters and Words from Sunburst Technology

Reading-readiness provides assessment reports as students: learn the order of alphabet, organize words and objects by initial consonant sounds, match rhyming words and homophones, match onsets and rimes, identify short and long vowel sounds.

This reading-readiness program provides you with assessment reports as your students:

    * learn the order of the alphabet
    * organize words and objects by initial consonant sounds
    * match rhyming words and homophones
    * build words by matching onsets and rimes
    * identify short and long vowel sounds
